{{bottom}}

===Interjection===
'''nee'''

# {{Geordie}} [[no]], used to express no as a quantity, i.e. not any, like german 'kein'. Compare with [[na]].
#: ''"'''Nee''' way man!"'' (No way)
#: ''"There's '''nee''' water!"'' (There's no water)

